snippet.title: TERRA MEMORIA - Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
After the rhythm game Old School Musical, La Moutarde is back with the #RPG Terra Memoria!
A small team of 6 quirky adventurers moved into our dear villagers' inn! They’re packing up for a very special journey through the world of Terra.
Wishlist now: https://swll.to/temanncmt
